{
  "meta": {
    "type": "chatter",
    "version": "0.2.0",
    "description": "行驶中车内日常对话池（比阿特丽克斯·波特风格重写版）。speaker: taoxia/linli; response 可选。"
  },
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "id": "CHAT_001",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "路上好安静啊……以前这条路上还能碰到别的车，像蚂蚁排队一样。现在只剩我们了。",
      "weight": 50,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……蚂蚁排队也有散的时候。但总会再排起来。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_002",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "温室社区的番茄罐头为什么那么受欢迎？明明味道一般啊。大概是因为红色在灰色的世界里太显眼了。",
      "weight": 50,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_003",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……油压表刚才跳了一下。像一只受惊的小鸟。可能是路面震动，先记一下。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_004",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "我在货箱里发现一张旧巧克力包装纸。闻起来还有一点点甜味——像昨天做的一个很远的梦。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……别翻货物。不过那张纸你留着吧。偶尔闻闻也不错。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_005",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "这段路的路基还算结实。以前应该是省道。路面上的裂缝像老树的纹路——还在长，但没有散。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": ["main_road", "highway"],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_006",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "废墟游民营地的人看我们的眼神像在打量一只飞进鸡窝的麻雀——不太欢迎，但也没有赶走。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_007",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "林砾，你有没有想过以后不跑商了做什么？比如开一个修车铺？门口种一棵树的那种。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.8],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……没想过。车能跑就继续跑。树能种就种。不用选。",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_008",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……天色不太好。云层厚得像棉被。希望不是辐射云。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": ["shortcut", "hazard"],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_009",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "出发啦！今天的阳光特别好——像是从窗户里偷偷溜进来的小猫，软软的、暖暖的。",
      "weight": 60,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 0.15],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_010",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "快到了吧？我已经开始想象卸完货之后的罐头汤了——罐头汤不高级，但比什么都没有好。",
      "weight": 55,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.8, 1.0],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……先把货交了再说。汤不会跑。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_011",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "轮胎磨损比预期快了一点……就像鞋子磨薄了底。下次该换备件了。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.4, 0.9],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_012",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "你知道吗，钟楼那边有个老爷爷收集了整整一墙的旧唱片。那些唱片像一片片黑色的池塘，里面藏着从前的声音。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 10,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["ch2_started"],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_013",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "陶夏，别把脚搁在仪表台上。仪表台不是脚垫。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "好嘛好嘛~但仪表台上晒太阳很舒服嘛，像窗台上的猫一样~",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1, "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_014",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "这条路两边都是旧楼，像一排排合上的旧书——不知道里面写了什么故事。开快点吧？我总觉得那些楼在看我们。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": ["shortcut", "hazard"],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_015",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "刚才路过的那片废墟好大……以前大概是个商场吧？想象一下里面曾经人来人往的样子——像蚁丘一样热闹。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.3, 0.7],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_016",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……走一半了。油耗正常。路也正常。天也正常。一切正常。",
      "weight": 50,
      "duration": 5,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.45, 0.55],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_017",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "林砾你困不困？要不要我讲个笑话？……算了，我讲的笑话你从来不笑。你笑起来肯定像冰化了——一定很好看。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 10,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.8],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……讲吧。反正我也不会笑。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_018",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "到站前把送货单再对一遍。上次送错了两箱——那两箱萝卜在废墟放了三天，差点变成了腌菜。",
      "weight": 50,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.85, 1.0],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_019",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "你有没有觉得……每次离开一个地方，再回来的时候它都变了一点点？就像一棵树，你不在的时候它偷偷长了两片叶子。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.3, 0.7],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……人也是。每次跑一趟回来，你也偷偷多了一点什么。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_020",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……后视镜松了。下次停车我紧一下。就像松鼠的窝松了要修一样——不修的话，看后面的眼睛就歪了。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.1, 0.5],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_021",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "如果旧时代的人看到我们现在这样子——一辆焊了又焊的卡车装着半车罐头到处跑——他们会怎么想？大概会觉得……我们很努力。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 10,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.8],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_022",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……嗯？没事。刚走神了。在想一个零件的事。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.4, 0.9],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "什么零件？能告诉我吗？",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_023",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "我以前在钟楼看到过一本旧相册。里面的人笑得好开心，在海边。海是什么感觉呢？大概像一个特别大的、看不见边的湖。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 11,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["ch2_started"],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_024",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "肚子有点饿了……肚子叫的声音像一只不高兴的猫。还有多久到啊？",
      "weight": 50,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.5, 0.85],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……忍忍。猫饿了也不会倒下。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_025",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……这条小路比上次来的时候宽了一点。有人在维护。就像有人一直在给一条小溪清理落叶——水流得更畅了。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": ["path"],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_026",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "我在副驾发现了一颗螺丝。不知道从哪掉下来的……它孤零零地躺在坐垫上，像一粒没人要的种子。要紧吗？",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 8,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……给我看看。种子可以不管，螺丝不行。",
        "effect": { "relation_linli": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_027",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "速度保持在四十左右。这个路况不能更快了。就像一只兔子——跑得太快会看不到脚下的坑。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": ["shortcut", "path"],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_028",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "你说，如果有天所有路都修好了，世界是不是就算恢复正常了？路连在一起，人也就连在一起了吧。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 10,
      "edge_types": ["main_road"],
      "progress_range": [0.2, 0.8],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……也许吧。路好走了，走的人就多了。走的人多了，故事就多了。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_029",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "下次路过温室的时候，帮我带一株薄荷苗回来好不好？我想种在车里。车里有一点点绿的话，开长途就不会那么困。",
      "weight": 35,
      "duration": 9,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": {
        "text": "……车里种不活。但你可以试试。试试不亏。就像种子掉在石头缝里——万一呢。",
        "effect": { "relation_taoxia": 1 }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_030",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……前面有段下坡。坐稳了。像坐滑梯一样——不过我们的滑梯是带轮子的。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 6,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0.3, 0.7],
      "required_flags": [],
      "forbidden_flags": [],
      "response": null
    },
    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_001",
      "speaker": "taoxia",
      "text": "沈禾说他们今年种的番茄比去年甜。她说可能是水质变好了。我咬了一口——确实甜。甜得像小时候偷吃的糖果。",
      "weight": 45,
      "duration": 10,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["prologue_done"],
      "forbidden_flags": ["ch2_started"],
      "response": null
