    {
      "id": "CHAT_CH1_002",
      "speaker": "linli",
      "text": "……温室到废墟这条路，我已经能闭着眼开了。闭着眼也知道哪块石头会颠。",
      "weight": 40,
      "duration": 7,
      "edge_types": [],
      "progress_range": [0, 1],
      "required_flags": ["prologue_done"],
      "forbidden_flags": ["ch1_done"],
      "response": {
        "text": "那你闭着眼开试试？我帮你看着。",
